$interpreted: Hanbei: That bird-brain Sophie, she's still at it? Dillydallying around...
Hutchinson: Yup, probably still sulking. After all, you two just finished arguing.
Ru-yi: Hanbei's too mean to Sophie-poo!
Hanbei: Hey, I'm just speaking the truth. We're a small circus. If we perform too long in the same place, the crowd's gonna get bored.
Hanbei: We'll also have no food to eat. Is that what you want?
Ru-yi: Yeah, but...Sophie's kinda right. All this traveling makes me feel like we don't have a home～
Hanbei: If she really wanted a home she would've married that rich fellow who was after her!
Hanbei: He even had a new home made for her.
Hutchinson: She didn't mean anything by it. She just felt like she was being forced...
Ru-yi: A girl's gotta marry the right one!
Hanbei: That'd be great, I just hope...that fairy tale her father used to tell doesn't come true.
Hanbei: When the time comes, she won't even be able to tell it's her true love.
Hutchinson: Mr. Morgan used to talk about the false king and the one that was lost...
Hutchinson: Come on now, she's only seventeen.
Hanbei: You think that's gonna happen again? Another handsome guy that appears out of nowhere and needs to be saved?
Hanbei: Bird-brain Sophie is definitely——
Elio: Uhh...
Hanbei: ...
Ru-yi: Oooh, handsome~
Hutchinson: Speak of the Devil...
Sophie: Ahh...so...heavy...
Sophie: Hanbei. Hutchinson, Ru-yi!
Sophie: This person needs help! Help me!
Elio: No...he's your uncle...father!
Ru-yi: Huh? So is it uncle or father?
Elio: ...Did you hear what I said?
Ru-yi: Shhhh! Quiet! I'm hiding from Sophie...
Sophie: Ru-yi!
Sophie: You're up next. Get ready!
Ru-yi: I don't wanna! I'm just a poor, old, sickly whale...it's so dry out there...If I keep spouting water, I'll dry up like a prune!
Sophie: It's just a little water. Quit hiding out in the tent all day, not getting any sun...
Sophie: You're awake!
Elio: Yeah. Thanks for yesterday. You helped me get away. You didn't have to take me in.
Sophie: No, no, it' s okay. I'm used to helping!
Elio: You're very kind.
Ru-yi: Come on now. Sophie, we know what you're up to...
Thug: Ha! A bunch of misfits! What kind of crappy circus is this?
Sophie: This is...Hanbei's prop...
Thug: Eh, who's in charge here?
Elio: Wait a sec, you——
Sophie: Ringmaster here. Morgan's Marvelous Circus, ATTEN-HUT!
Elio: Morgan...
Sophie: Morgan is my father's name. He created this circus.
Sophie: Hanbei. Hutchinson, and Ru-yi were all born with defects. After they were abandoned, my father took them in.
Elio: I see...he must have been a good man.
Sophie: ...Yeah. If trying to make everybody happy is good.
Elio: Huh?
Hutchinson: Sophie! A fan wants your signature!
Sophie: Cominggg～
